    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <strong>What happens when the Chosen One simply refuses to be Chosen?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It matters not that a terrifying evil has descended on this world. It matters not that entire towns are being wiped out on a daily basis. It matters not that they're asking for you to save them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because your washing machine is busted, and you <i>really</i> need to get home and do some laundry. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Questing is equal parts love letter and satire, influenced by classic 16-bit action-adventure games, such as A Link to the Past, Chrono Trigger, and Secret of Mana.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take on monsters in a unique Pong-meets-Bullet-Hell battle system: </strong><br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/68192f53298bf3d47c7282d9d9a5fd92.poster.avif?t=1754665485\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/68192f53298bf3d47c7282d9d9a5fd92.webm?t=1754665485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/68192f53298bf3d47c7282d9d9a5fd92.mp4?t=1754665485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a world of odd characters, dangerous perils, and intriguing secrets on your journey:</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/da6ac666041a10158f6a6349a07d5202.poster.avif?t=1754665485\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/da6ac666041a10158f6a6349a07d5202.webm?t=1754665485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/da6ac666041a10158f6a6349a07d5202.mp4?t=1754665485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve terribly tricky puzzles along the way:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/6416123fbd5c52fd3be09a49d04ef90c.poster.avif?t=1754665485\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/6416123fbd5c52fd3be09a49d04ef90c.webm?t=1754665485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/6416123fbd5c52fd3be09a49d04ef90c.mp4?t=1754665485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And definitely don’t try to help people or save the world.<u><strong></strong></u><br><br><br><br><br>  <br> After all, <i>you're no hero.</i>  <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras/76e58d5b130f73beb084f33292a5957c.avif?t=1754665485\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087670/extras_big/76e58d5b130f73beb084f33292a5957c.avif?t=1754665485 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
